<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>At a Glance: debis AG</TITLE></HEAD><BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF"><P><CENTER><A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A><A HREF="../group_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/komp_kl.gif"></A><A HREF="system_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A><BR><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><FONT SIZE=+3><B>debis AG</B></FONT><P><TABLE><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275><IMG SRC="pics/service.gif"><TD WIDTH=20><TD VALIGN=MIDDLE ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275><FONT SIZE=+1><B>"Spare us a moment of your time.<br>It will save you a lot more."</B></FONT><TR><TD><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275>Why let the daily workload of running your business turn into an uphill battle? Our approach to outsourcing lets you trim time-consuming, recurring tasks from your agenda with the reassurance that the work will be done right the first time and every time - and to the same high standards.<br><TD WIDTH=20><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>That's because we're immediately up to speed with your own workflows and bring the kind of commitment and know-how to our work that allows us to hit the ground running and you to focus on your core business - and hone your competitive edge in the global marketplace.<tr><td><br><tr><TD colspan=3 VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="debis2_e.htm">More about debis AG</A></TABLE><P><IMG WIDTH=250 H