<TITLE>Das Daimler-Benz Geschichtsspiel</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="/history/spiel1/mexpics/db_back1.jpg" LINK="#2060a0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#e0e0ff">

<P>
<center>
<A HREF="/history/spiel1/../index_g.htm"><IMG SRC="/history/spiel1/mexpics/db_home.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="89" HEIGHT="33"></A>
