<HTML>

<HEAD><TITLE>Help</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY background="../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF">
<P>

<CENTER>

<A HREF="../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../icons/db_home.gif"></A>
<A HREF="../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/db_such.gif"></A>
<A HREF="../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> 
<BR>

<IMG SRC="../lines/db_592.gif"><P>


<TABLE border=0>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=150><IMG SRC="../icons/help.gif">
<TD WIDTH=20>
<TD ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=280><b><FONT SIZE=+4>Help</FONT></b>
</TABLE>
<P>

<TABLE border=0><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=right WIDTH=275>
<B>User Guidance and Navigation</B><BR>
in our wide-based service is as easy as you can imagine.
After choosing a language on the welcome page you come onto the homepage itself that provides direct links to the program's individual features and sections.
<BR>
<TD WIDTH=20>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=left WIDTH=275>The small icons at the head and corresponding text links at the foot of any page lead to the most important basic functions.<BR>
Besides providing easy navigation these icons also serve as a useful orientation aid. <BR> 

<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>
<IMG WIDTH=250 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../lines/db_250.gif"><P>
<A HREF="#db"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../icons/db_home.gif"></A>
<A HREF="#submenu"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/spotkl.gif"></A>
<A HREF="#weiter"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A>
<A HREF="#hoch"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/menu_up.gif"></A>
<A HREF="#suche"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/db_such.gif"></A>
<A HREF="#mail"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/mailkl.gif"></A>
<A HREF="#hilfe"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/helpkl.gif"></A><BR>
<P>

<IMG WIDTH=250 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../lines/db_250.gif"><P>
<TABLE border=0>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=120>
<TD WIDTH=10>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=380> 
<B>The Icons and what they mean</B><BR>
<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>

<A NAME="db"></A>
<TABLE border=0>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=120>
<IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../icons/db_home.gif"> 
<TD WIDTH=10>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=380> 
The Daimler-Benz Icon brings you straight back to the homepage.<BR>
<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>

<A NAME="submenu"></A>
<TABLE border=0>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=120>
<IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/spotkl.gif"> 
<TD WIDTH=10>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=380> 
The chapter-specific icons not only aid orientation, but also lead directly back to the current submenu.<BR>
<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>

<A NAME="weiter"></A>
<TABLE border=0>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=120>
<IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/menu_rig.gif">
<TD WIDTH=10>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=380> 
You can flick through all the pages in a section using the 'forward' arrow.<BR>
<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>

<A NAME="hoch"></A>
<TABLE border=0>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=120>
<IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/menu_up.gif">
<TD WIDTH=10>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=380> 
The upward arrow is useful when using links within a program section - it links back to the next higher menu.<BR>
<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>

<A NAME="suche"></A>
<TABLE border=0>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=120>
<IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/db_such.gif">
<TD WIDTH=10>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=380> 
The magnifying glass represents our search-function. It allows you to browse easily through the complete content of our server.<BR>
<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>

<A NAME="mail"></A>
<TABLE border=0>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=120>
<IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/mailkl.gif">
<TD WIDTH=10>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=380> 
The envelope symbol connects you to our dialogue features (email, ordering).<BR>
<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>

<A NAME="hilfe"></A>
<TABLE border=0>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=120>
<IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../icons/helpkl.gif">
<TD WIDTH=10>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=380> 
That's how easy it is to get around our program - you've found our help function already!<BR>
<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>

<IMG WIDTH=250 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../lines/db_250.gif"><P>

<TABLE border=0><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=right WIDTH=275>
<B>Images</B><BR>
To keep data quantities to a minimum we optimise all our images for online use. Clicking on reduced images allows
<BR>
<TD WIDTH=20>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=left WIDTH=275>
<A HREF="pics/fotoq1.jpg"><IMG ALIGN=LEFT VSPACE=3 HSPACE=-2 WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=80 border=0 SRC="pics/fotoq1.gif"></A><IMG ALIGN=LEFT VSPACE=3 HSPACE=-2 WIDTH=6 HEIGHT=80 SRC="../icons/abstand.gif">you to view the full-sized versions.<BR> 

<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>

<IMG WIDTH=250 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../lines/db_250.gif"><P>

<TABLE border=0><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=right WIDTH=275>
<B>Your path to new technologies</B><P>
Our online service takes advantage of the newest, most exciting and innovative technologies. As older browsers may not allow you to access certain features we recommend that you install the most up-to-date browser version and plug-ins (functional extensions).
<TD WIDTH=20>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=left WIDTH=275>
This application is optimised for viewing with the 
<A HREF="http://home.netscape.com/comprod/upgrades/index.html">Netscape 2.0</A> browser (simply click on this link to download and install the latest Netscape version), and its <A HREF="http://home.netscape.com/comprod/products/navigator/version_2.0/plugins/index.html">Plug-Ins</A>. Some of the information in this service as well as original documents, including our environmental report, are also available as .pdf files, which can be viewed with the Acrobat-Amber Plug-In.<BR>

<TR><TD><BR>
</TABLE>
<p><br>


<IMG SRC="../lines/db_592.gif"><P>



