<HTML>



<HEAD><TITLE>At a Glance: debis Assurance Broking</TITLE></HEAD>







<BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF">



<P>







<CENTER>







<A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A>



<A HREF="../group_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/komp_kl.gif"></A>



<A HREF="tradin_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A>



<A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A>



<A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A>



<BR>



<IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P>







<FONT SIZE=+3><B>debis Assurance Broking</B></FONT>



<P>







<TABLE>



<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275><IMG SRC="pics/insuranc.gif">



<TD WIDTH=20>



<TD VALIGN=MIDDLE ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>



<FONT SIZE=+1><B>"Assurance is good.<br>
Preassurance is better.
"</B></FONT>



<TR><TD>



<TR>



<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275>



Protecting a company against all eventualities can be an expensive proposition. Our Risk EngIneering can provide just the kind of reassurance you need. The first thing we do is to identify all imaginable risk factors. Then we evaluate and quantify them.<br>
<TD WIDTH=20>



<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>
The next step is to prepare a catalogue of measures for minimising precisely these risks, and where possible even eliminating them altogether. We then put together a package tailored to provide the assurance cover you need for the remaining risk. 
<tr><td><br>



<tr><TD colspan=3 VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="insur2_e.htm">More about debis Assurance Broking</A>



</TABLE>



