<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>At a Glance: debis Trading</TITLE></HEAD><BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF"><P><CENTER><A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A><A HREF="../group_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/komp_kl.gif"></A><A HREF="mobile_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A><BR><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><FONT SIZE=+3><B>debis Trading</B></FONT><P><TABLE><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275><IMG SRC="pics/trading.gif"><TD WIDTH=20><TD VALIGN=MIDDLE ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275><FONT SIZE=+1><B>"Even the hardest<br>currencies can count us."</B></FONT><TR><TD><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275>Some currencies can prove a tough nut to crack for countries without sufficient reserves. That is why debis introduced a financial instrument that creates the leverage it takes to deal with the hardest currencies: countertrading.<br><TD WIDTH=20><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>In-depth analysis of trade practies, barriers and opportunities helps us to develop concepts for optimal commodities trading. Thats how you can turn the liability of unpredictable resources into a hard currency asset.<tr><td><br><tr><TD colspan=3 VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="tradi2_e.htm">More about debis Trading</A></TABLE><P><br><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><TABLE><TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=550><H5><A HREF