<HEAD><TITLE>At a Glance: Mercedes-Benz</TITLE></HEAD>



<BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF">

<P>



<CENTER>



<A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../group_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/komp_kl.gif"></A>

<A HREF="pkw_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> 

<A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A>

<BR>



<IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P>



<FONT SIZE=+3><B>Mercedes-Benz</B></FONT>

<P>



<TABLE>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275><IMG SRC="pics/mb_e1.gif"><BR>

<TD WIDTH=20>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>Since July 1989, Mercedes-Benz has been responsible for the entire motor vehicle business within the Daimler-Benz Group. As per 31 December 1995, the company employed some 139,700 people at its fourteen domestic passenger car and commercial vehicle plants, in its 43 company-owned sales and service outlets and at the headquarters of Mercedes-Benz AG.<BR>

<TR><TD>

<TR>


<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275>Including the production and sales companies outside Germany, some 197,200 people throughout the group worked for "the youngest German motor manufacturer with the longest tradition" at the end of 1995.<BR>

<TD WIDTH=20>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>


Mercedes-Benz is a global player with over 50 production and assembly plants and some 6,300 sales and service outlets throughout the world. The vehicles with the three-pointed star are sold in some 190 countries.<BR>

</TABLE>

<P><br>



<IMG WIDTH=250 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_250.gif"><P>



<TABLE>



<TR><TD colspan=3 align=center><A HREF="bofm/bofm_e.htm"><font size=+1><I><B>The Board of Management</B></I></FONT></A><BR>

<TR><TD colspan=3 align=center><A HREF="data_e.htm"><font size=+1><I><B>Facts and Figures</B></I></FONT></A><BR>

<tr><td><br>



<TR>

<TD ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275 valign=top><A HREF="pkw_e.htm"><font size=+1><I><B>Passenger Cars</B></I></FONT></A><BR>

<TD width=20>

<TD ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275 valign=top><A HREF="nfz_e.htm"><I><font size=+1><B>Commercial Vehicles</B></FONT></I></A><BR>



<TR>

<TD colspan=3 align=center><A HREF="diesel_e.htm"><I><font size=+1><B>Diesel Drives</B></FONT></I></A><BR>

<TR><TD><BR>
<tr>
<TD colspan=3 align=center><A HREF="http://www.mercedes-benz.com/e/mbe1.htm"><I><font size=+1><B>to the Mercedes-Benz WWW-Server</B></FONT></I></A><BR>

</TABLE>

