<HTML>

<HEAD><TITLE>At a Glance: Diesel Drives</TITLE></HEAD>



<BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF">

<P>



<CENTER>



<A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../group_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/komp_kl.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../dasa/dasa_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> 

<A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A>

<BR>



<IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P>



<FONT SIZE=+3><B>Diesel Drives</B></FONT>

<P>



<TABLE>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275><IMG SRC="pics/diesel.gif"><BR>

<TD WIDTH=20>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>The diesel drives division combines MTU Motoren- und Turbinenunion Friedrichshafen GmbH and ist subsidiaries.

These companies develop, produce and sell high-quality drive and propulsion systems for ships, locomotives and heavy trucks as well as engines for power generating equipment. The product range is based on compact high-performance diesel engines covering a range of 40 to 7,400 kW.<BR>

<TR><TD>

<TR>



<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275>The range of products and services also includes gas turbines, power transmission systems, electronic monitoring and control systems as well, in future, as gas-powered engines. The focal areas for business activity are markets<BR>

<TD WIDTH=20>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>



outside Germany, especially in Asia. In the expanding commercial market, MTU Friedrichshafen leads the world in propulsion units for highspeed passenger ferries and is also Number 1 for yachts with a length in excess of 30 metres.<BR>

</TABLE>

<P><br>



<IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P>



<TABLE>

<TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=550>

