<HEAD><TITLE>At a Glance: Mercedes-Benz Cars</TITLE></HEAD>



<BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF">

<P>



<CENTER>



<A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../group_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/komp_kl.gif"></A>

<A HREF="nfz_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A>

<A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> 

<A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A>

<BR>



<IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P>



<FONT SIZE=+3><B>Passenger Cars</B></FONT>

<P>



<TABLE>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275><IMG SRC="pics/pkw.gif"><BR>

<TD WIDTH=20>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>Mercedes-Benz sees itself as an exclusive manufacturer of premium cars in all attractive segments of the market. The company's internationally unique tradition as an innovative producer of high-quality cars is to be consistently continued into the next millennium. 

<TR><TD>

<TR>



<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275>At the beginning of 1993, the company announced the far-reaching re-orientation of its strategic product policy. In addition to the current model series in the core segments of the C, E, S and SL-classes, Mercedes-Benz will in the future also offer the A-class, positioned<BR>

<TD WIDTH=20>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>

below the C-class, the V-class (MPV), the small SLK sports car and the All Activity Vehicle. Together with the Swiss company SMH (Schweizerische Gesellschaft f&uuml;r Mikroelektronik und Uhrenindustrie), Mercedes-Benz also plans to produce a two-seater city car (Smart).<BR>

</TABLE>

<P><br>

<A HREF="pkw2_e.htm">More about Passenger Cars</A>
<p>

<A HREF="http://www.mercedes-benz.com/e/mbe1.htm"><I><font size=+1><B>to the Mercedes-Benz WWW-Server</B></FONT></I></A><BR>
