<BR>



<IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P>



<FONT SIZE=+3><B>Commercial Vehicles</B></FONT>

<P>



<TABLE>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275><IMG ALIGN=rightWIDTH=200 HEIGHT=160 border=0 SRC="pics/nfz.gif"><BR>

<TD WIDTH=20>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>The diversified range of Mercedes-Benz commercial vehicles extends from vans with two tonnes permissible gross weight to 48-tonners, including a multitude of special versions, and thus meets virtually all requirements arising from all conceivable applications. In addition, there are urban and country buses and touring coaches, the Unimog range and industrial engines for a wide range of applications.<BR>

<TR><TD>

<TR>



<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275>The Commercial Vehicle Business Unit employs some 33,100 people in Germany (excluding EvoBus and Mercedes-Benz<BR>

<TD WIDTH=20>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>


Lenkungen GmbH), while the foreign production companies together have a workforce of approx. 37,300.<BR>

</TABLE>

