<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>At a Glance: Daimler-Benz Aerospace Defense and Civil Systems</TITLE></HEAD><BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF"><P><CENTER><A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A><A HREF="../group_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/komp_kl.gif"></A><A HREF="propul_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A><BR><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><FONT SIZE=+3><B>Defense and Civil Systems</B></FONT><P><TABLE><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275><IMG SRC="pics/civil.gif" WIDTH=200 HEIGHT=280 ><BR><TD WIDTH=20><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>The Defense and Civil Systems Group is headed by Werner Heinzmann. The group is divided into LFK-Lenkflugk&ouml;rpersysteme GmbH and the divisions Information and Communication Systems and Sensor Systems, as well as two profit centers in the fields of Waste Disposal and Logistics. Defense systems, instrumental to security and peace, remain a core business of Daimler-Benz Aerospace, even though security policy has changed.<BR><TR><TD><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=275>The group utilizes the expertise gained in defense technology to develop and expand new technological areas for civil products and systems. In addition, <BR><TD WIDTH=20><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=275>the business group has been restructured and adjusted to the altered prevailing conditions the German defense industry has to face.<