<html>

<head>
<title>Consolidated Interim Report: Daimler-Benz Aerospace (DASA)</title>

</head>

<body background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" text="#000000" link="#2060A0" vlink="#606060" alink="#E0E0FF">
<p align=center><a href="../../index_e.htm"><img src="../../icons/db_home.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=89 height=33></a> <a href="../facts_e.htm"><img src="../../icons/factskl.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=54 height=44></a> <a href="debis_e.htm"><img src="../../icons/menu_rig.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=54 height=44></a> <a href="../../search/search_e.htm"><img src="../../icons/db_such.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=54 height=44></a> <a href="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><img src="../../icons/mailkl.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=54 height=44></a> <a href="../../help/help_e.htm"><img src="../../icons/helpkl.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=54 height=44></a> <br>
<img src="../../lines/db_592.gif" align=bottom width=592 height=16></p>
<p align=center><font size=5><b>Daimler-Benz Aerospace (DASA)</b></font> </p>
<div align=center><center>
<table>
<tr><td valign=bottom><font size=2>DM amounts in millions</font> </td><td></td><td align=right valign=bottom width=130><b>01-09/96</b></td><td></td><td align=right width=130><b>01-09/95</b></td></tr>
<tr><td align=right valign=top width=220></td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=5><hr>
</td></tr>
<tr><td>Revenues </td><td></td><td align=right>8,278</td><td></td><td align=right>8,914</td><td><sup><font size=1>1)</font></sup></td></tr>
<tr><td>Incoming orders </td><td></td><td align=right>13,563</td><td></td><td align=right>7,182</td><td><sup><font size=1>2)</font></sup> </td></tr>
<tr><td>Employees <font size=2>(9/30)</font> </td><td></td><td align=right>45,573</td><td></td><td align=right>47,732</td><td><sup><font size=1>2)</font></sup> </td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=5><hr>
</td></tr>
</table>
<p></p>
</center></div>
<div align=center><center>
<table width=500>
<tr><td><font size=2>1) Adjusted for significant changes in consolidation, revenues amount to DM 7.009 mill.<br>
2)	Figures have been adjusted to take account of significant changes in consolidation.</font></td></tr>
</table>
<p></p>
</center></div>
<div align=center><center>
<table>
<tr><td valign=top width=380>In 1996, Dasa resolutely continued to pursue the measures it 
had introduced to improve profitability. In late August an 
agreement for permanent cost reductions was reached 
between management and employee representatives at 
Daimler-Benz Aerospace Airbus GmbH, as had been 
achieved earlier for other divisions. Thus Dasa is also further 
reducing its dependence on the US dollar.<p>The corporate unit&#146;s revenues for January to September 1996 
were up 18% as compared with the corresponding value for 
1995, reaching a total of DM 8.3 billion. The growth was 
predominantly contributed by Propulsion Systems (up 48%), 
which in addition to a revival of business in general also 
recorded higher invoicing for jet engines, and by Space 
Systems (up 51%), where the projects XMM (X-Ray 
Multi-Mirror Mission) and Envisat generated significantly 
higher revenues. Business volume grew only slightly in the 
Aircraft division (up 5%) and in Defense and Civil Systems 
(up 3%). Because of the noticeable increase in deliveries of jet 
engine components, the revenues generated in the USA rose 
by 37%. A significant increase was also reported in Germany 
(up 11%), the other EU countries (up 18%), and in the other 
markets (up 13%).</p>
<p>The high demand for Airbus aircraft and propulsion systems, 
coupled with several large orders in the Space Systems 
division, meant that incoming orders at Dasa were up 89% to 
DM 13.6 billion. At Airbus alone, orders in the first nine 
months, at 269 aircraft, were as high as in the last three years 
together. In Defense and Civil Systems, incoming orders grew 
in the sectors of pilot and information systems, equipment for 
crisis response forces, and Nortel Dasa Network Systems in 
particular.</p>
</td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
<p align=center><font size=2><img src="../../lines/db_592.gif" align=bottom width=592 height=16></font></p>
<div align=center><center>
<table>
<tr><td align=center width=550><h5><a href="dasa_g.htm"><font size=2>[&#160;<i>Deutsch</i>&#160;]</font></a><font size=2> </font><a href="../../index_e.htm"><font size=2>[&#160;<i>Home</i>&#160;]</font></a><font size=2> </font><a href="../facts_e.htm"><font size=2>[&#160;<i>Facts &amp; Figures</i>&#160;]</font></a><font size=2> </font><a href="debis_e.htm"><font size=2>[&#160;<i>Next</i>&#160;]</font></a><font size=2> </font><a href="../../search/search_e.htm"><font size=2>[&#160;<i>Search</i>&#160;]</font></a><font size=2> </font><a href="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><font size=2>[&#160;<i>Dialog</i>&#160;]</font></a><font size=2> </font><a href="../../help/help_e.htm"><font size=2>[&#160;<i>Help</i>&#160;]</font></a><font size=2> </font></h5>
</td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
