esearch.</TD><TD WIDTH="20"></TD><TD WIDTH="275" VALIGN="TOP"><FONT SIZE=+1>3/22/96<BR><B><I><A HREF="text/60322_e.htm">ZEBRA under the bonnet</A></I></B></FONT><BR>In the ZEBRA battery is an environmentally-friendly source of power whichis also very safe.<BR></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="275">&nbsp;</TD><TD WIDTH="20">&nbsp;</TD><TD WIDTH="275">&nbsp;</TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN="RIGHT" WIDTH="275" VALIGN="TOP"><FONT SIZE=+1>3/13/96<BR><B><I><A HREF="text/60313_e.htm">Gathering rust</A></I></B></FONT><BR>Daimler-Benz researchers are investigating the processes governing microbialcorrosion on aluminium alloy aircraft parts. </TD><TD WIDTH="20"></TD><TD WIDTH="275" VALIGN="TOP"><FONT SIZE=+1>3/5/96<BR><B><I><A HREF="text/60305_e.htm">The way through the mountains</A></I></B></FONT><BR>Tests into computer-controlled automated driving systems. </TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="275">&nbsp;</TD><TD WIDTH="20">&nbsp;</TD><TD WIDTH="275">&nbsp;</TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN="RIGHT" WIDTH="275" VALIGN="TOP"><FONT SIZE=+1>2/29/96<BR><B><I><A HREF="text/60229_e.htm">Softener for exhaust gas</A></I></B></FONT><BR>Zeolites monitor the gas concentration in exhaust. </TD><TD WIDTH="20"></TD><TD WIDTH="275" VALIGN="TOP"><FONT SIZE=+1>2/22/96<BR><B><I><A HREF="text/60222_e.htm">Engine with a view</A></I></B></FONT><BR>New insight into the combustion process thanks to a &quot;see-through&quot;engine. </TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="275">&nbsp;</TD><TD WIDTH="20">&nbsp;</TD><TD WIDTH="275">&nbsp;</TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN="RIGHT" WIDTH="275" VALIGN="TOP"><FONT SIZE=+1>2/21/96<BR><B><I><A HREF="text/60221_e.htm">The virtual car that deceives <BR>virtually all our senses</A></I></B></FONT><BR>A stereo vision data helmet takes its wearer into the cockpit of a car inwhich nothing is real except the illusion. </TD><TD WIDTH="20"></TD><TD WIDTH="275" VALIGN="TOP"><FONT SIZE=+1>2/20/96<BR><B><I><A HREF="text/60220_e.htm">Easy victim: <BR>the microchip</A></I></B></FONT><BR>Daimler-Benz researchers maintain a round-the-clock alert to banish allimpurities from the clean room </TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="275">&nbsp;</TD><TD WIDTH="20">&nbsp;</TD><TD WIDTH="275">&nbsp;</TD></TR></TABLE><IMG SRC="../lines/db_592.gif" WIDTH="592" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></P><P ALIGN=CENTER><TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="2" CELLPADDING="0"><TR><TD ALIGN="CENTER" WIDTH="550"><H5><A HREF="newspl_g.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Deutsch</I>&nbsp;]</A> <A HREF="../index_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Home</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="news_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Research&amp;Technology</I>&nbsp;]</A> <AHREF="../search/search_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Search</I>&nbsp;]</A> <A HREF="../mail/mail_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Dialog</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../help/help_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Help</I>&nbsp;]</A> </H5></TD></TR></TABLE></P><ADDRESS ALIGN=CENTER>&copy; Daimler-Benz, last update: 10/01/1996</ADDRESS></BODY></HTML>
