<HEAD>
<TITLE>The rules</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="/history/game1/mexpics/db_back1.jpg" LINK="#2060a0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#e0e0ff">

<P>
<center>
<A HREF="http://www.daimler-benz.com/index_e.htm"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/db_home.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="89" HEIGHT="33"></A>
<A HREF="/history/game1/script/spot.cgi?src=rg01&dest=st01&hist=anf-st01&status=0000"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/i_menu1.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="44"></A>
<A HREF="/history/game1/script/spot.cgi?src=rg01&dest=in03&hist=anf-st01&status=0000"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/i_next1.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="44"></A>
<A HREF="http://www.daimler-benz.com/search/search_e.htm"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/db_such.gif"BORDER="0" WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="44" ></A>
<A HREF="http://www.daimler-benz.com/mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/mailkl.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="44" ></A>
<A HREF="http://www.daimler-benz.com/help/help_e.htm"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/helpkl.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="54"HEIGHT="44" ></A>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/db_592.gif" WIDTH="592" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></P>


<TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
<tr><TD colspan=5><IMG SRC="/history/game1/fram_1.gif" WIDTH=571 HEIGHT=57></TD>
<TR>
	<TD><IMG SRC="/history/game1/fram_3.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=340></TD>
	<TD>
	<TD  WIDTH=440 ><FONT SIZE=+2>Rules of the game</FONT><P>

Click on <I>'Play'</I> to start. The game is made up of text, image and video clippings.
The texts and pictures contain the information you need to solve the four riddles.<P>
The objective is to answer the four questions found behind the question marks.<BR>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="/history/game1/bfrag1.jpg"></CENTER><BR>
For each question you must choose one of the answers given - only one is correct. When you think you know the right answer, mark it and then send it off by clicking the <I>'selection made'</I> button.<P><A HREF="/history/game1/script/spot.cgi?src=rg01&dest=in03&hist=anf-st01&status=0000"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/weiter_1.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT ALT="weiter" BORDER=0></A>
	<TD>
	<TD><IMG SRC="/history/game1/fram_2.gif" WIDTH=48 HEIGHT=340 ALIGN=RIGHT></TD>
<TR>
<TD colspan=5><IMG SRC="/history/game1/fram_4.gif" WIDTH=571 HEIGHT=54></TD>
</TABLE>
<P><BR>
<IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/db_592.gif"></P>
