<HEAD>
<TITLE>The prizes</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="/history/game1/mexpics/db_back1.jpg" LINK="#2060a0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#e0e0ff">

<P>
<center>
<A HREF="http://www.daimler-benz.com/index_e.htm"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/db_home.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="89" HEIGHT="33"></A>
<A HREF="/history/game1/script/spot.cgi?src=pr01&dest=st01&hist=anf-st01&status=0000"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/i_menu1.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="44"></A>
<A HREF="http://www.daimler-benz.com/search/search_e.htm"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/db_such.gif"BORDER="0" WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="44" ></A>
<A HREF="http://www.daimler-benz.com/mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/mailkl.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="44" ></A>
<A HREF="http://www.daimler-benz.com/help/help_e.htm"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/helpkl.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="54"HEIGHT="44" ></A> <BR>
<IMG SRC="/history/game1/mexpics/db_592.gif" WIDTH="592" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></P>


<TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
<tr><TD colspan=5><IMG SRC="/history/game1/fram_1.gif" WIDTH=571 HEIGHT=57></TD>
<TR>
	<TD WIDTH=40><IMG SRC="/history/game1/fram_3.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=340><BR><IMG SRC="/history/game1/fram_3.gif" WIDTH=51 HEIGHT=340></TD>
	<TD WIDTH=16>
	<TD WIDTH=420>
<FONT SIZE=+2>The prizes</FONT><P>
<!-- **********************************************************************-->
What you can win and what you have to do for it:- we are giving away some great prizes to 20 lucky participants who find the right solutions to the Daimler-Benz History Game. You will only be entered in the draw if you answer all four questions correctly.
<P>
The prizes are:<P>
1st place: A 1:8 scale model of the Benz patented motor car (value 495,- DM)<P>
2nd - 20th place: Choice of either a CD-ROM* on the history of Mercedes-Benz (value 99,- DM), or a 1:24 scale model of the Benz Patent Motorcar (value 68,- DM)<P>
<FONT SIZE=-1>* only available in German</FONT>
<P>
The closing date for entries is January 12th 1997. The winners will be announced here at the WWW site. Employees of the Daimler-Benz concern are excluded. The judges decision is final and not subject to appeal.<BR>

Participants are only entered in the draw if they answer all four questions correctly.<P>
<A HREF="http://www.usm.de"><IMG SRC="/history/game1/usm_t.gif" BORDER=0 ALIGN=LEFT></A>
&nbsp;&nbsp;CD-ROM for Windows and Mac<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;The big history of the automobile<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;The multimedia encyclopaedia of all series and models<P>

