<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Environmental Report `96 - Projects: KEN for Zero Emissions</TITLE></HEAD><BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF"><P><CENTER><A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A><A HREF="../envir_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/envirokl.gif"></A><A HREF="../projek_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_up.gif"></A><A HREF="27_4_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A><BR><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><font size=+2><b>KEN for Zero Emissions</b></font><p><table><tr><td valign=top align=left width=380>The establishment of the Center for Zero-Emission Commercial Vehicle Expertise (known under its German acronym KEN) in Mannheim is a further feather in the cap of Mercedes-Benz-long a driving force behind research into low-pollution vehicles. Three million marks were allocated by the board for the start phase of the center alone. For the last few months, KEN developers have been concentrating not only on the zero-emission vehicle, but have also been working to improve conventional diesel and SI engines. After all, optimized combustion conditions, direct injection, and catalytic converter preheating represent a considerable reduction in exhaust fumes, even if they cannot eliminate them entirely. All-in-all, a step in the right direction.</table><p><br><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><TABLE><TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=550><H5><A HREF="27_3_g.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Deutsch</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../index_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Home</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../envir_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Environment</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../ub96_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Environmental Report '96</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../projek_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Projects</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="27_4_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Next</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Search</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Dialog</I>&nbsp;]</A>   <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Help</I>&nbsp;]</A></H5></TABLE><ADDRESS>&copy; Daimler-Benz, last update: 08/06/1996</ADDRESS><P></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
