<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Environmental Report &#180;96 - Highlights: Special Waste Cut By 600 Tonnes</TITLE></HEAD><BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF"><P><CENTER><A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A><A HREF="../envir_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/envirokl.gif"></A><A HREF="../schlag_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_up.gif"></A><A HREF="13_4_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A><BR><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><font size=+2><b>Special Waste Cut By 600 Tonnes</b></font><p><table><tr><td valign=top align=left width=380>In 1995, Mercedes-Benz's Untert&uuml;rkheim plant cut the special waste it produced by more than 600 tonnes to just 2000 tonnes. Thanks to internal de-watering and de-oiling, a particularly dramatic fall in the amount of sludge from the oil separation plant was recorded. In addition, disposable filter systems were replaced with long-life materials, and other special wastes were also significantly reduced. And this trend is set to continue with a bold plan to cut waste quantities at Untert&uuml;rkheim by a factor of four over the next few years. Success will depend heavily upon the direction taken, for example, by future legislation on the operating conditions for external recycling.</table><p><br><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><TABLE><TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=550><H5><A HREF="13_3_g.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Deutsch</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../index_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Home</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../envir_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Environment</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../ub96_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Environmental Report '96</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../schlag_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Spotlights</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="13_4_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Next</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Search</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Dialog</I>&nbsp;]</A>   <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Help</I>&nbsp;]</A></H5></TABLE><ADDRESS>&copy; Daimler-Benz, last update: 08/06/1996</ADDRESS><P></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
