<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Environmental Report `96 - Highlights: "Greening up the Gray-Belt"</TITLE></HEAD><BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF"><P><CENTER><A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A><A HREF="../envir_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/envirokl.gif"></A><A HREF="../schlag_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_up.gif"></A><A HREF="13_5_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A><BR><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><font size=+2><b>"Greening up the Gray-Belt"</b></font><p><table><tr><td valign=top align=left width=380><a href="../pics/13_4.jpg"><img align=left vspace=3 hspace=-2 width=100 height=80 border=0 src="../pics/13_4.gif"></a><img align=left vspace=3 hspace=-2 width=6 height=80 src="../../icons/abstand.gif">Just three years old and already in the honors' list: Participating in Nuremberg's "Greening up the Gray-Belt" competition, the Daimler-Benz subsidiary TEMIC (Telefunken Microelectronic GmbH) received a prize for "exemplary green design" in October 1995, awarded by the city's Environmental Department. For TEMIC green design means much more than just a touch of greenery. Indigenous trees and shrubs, wooded copses, grassy meadows and sandy areas all help provide a valuable habitat for wildlife. Water-permeable parking spaces prevent the desolation of the ground beneath. Finally, a huge company compost heap helps recycle biological waste.</table><p><br><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><TABLE><TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=550><H5><A HREF="13_4_g.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Deutsch</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../index_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Home</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../envir_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Environment</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../ub96_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Environmental Report '96</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../schlag_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Highlights</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="13_5_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Next</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Search</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Dialog</I>&nbsp;]</A>   <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Help</I>&nbsp;]</A></H5></TABLE><ADDRESS>&copy; Daimler-Benz, last update: 08/06/1996</ADDRESS><P></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
