<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Environmental Report '96 - Emissions</TITLE></HEAD><BODY background="../../icons/db_back1.jpg" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#2060A0" VLINK="#606060" ALINK="#E0E0FF"><P><CENTER><A HREF="../../index_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=89 HEIGHT=33 SRC="../../icons/db_home.gif"></A><A HREF="../envir_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/envirokl.gif"></A><A HREF="../schlag_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_up.gif"></A><A HREF="../daten_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/menu_rig.gif"></A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/db_such.gif"></A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/mailkl.gif"></A> <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=54 HEIGHT=44 SRC="../../icons/helpkl.gif"></A><BR><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><TABLE><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=360><font size=+2><b>Emissions</b></font><p>Immediately striking is an increase on the previous year of around 13.7 percent in total emissions registered under the "Solvents" category. The reason for this is that it was possible to collect data for certain solvents-mainly from disparate sources such as cleansing-for the first time in the year under review. The largest items here are the emissions from various sources in the Mercedes-Benz plant in Sindelfingen (426 tonnes) and MTU-Friedrichshafen (35 tonnes). The remaining chlorinated hydrocarbon emissions (15 tonnes in 1994, 9 tonnes in 1995) can be traced back to tetrachloroethane used to clean individual engine components at MTU-M&uuml;nchen and to dichloromethane used to strip the paint from aircraft in Oberpfaffenhofen.With the expiration of the exemption permit granted to Dasa for its CFC cleaning unit for electronic components in Ulm, the last plant of its kind in the group was closed down. CFCs are now only employed in older air conditioning units.<p>Responsibility for the remaining extremely low CFC emissions (0.01 tonnes) lies with leaks occurring in those older air conditioning and refrigeration installations which it has not been technically feasible to update.Traditional air pollutants such as dust, sulfur dioxide and nitrogen oxides have once again seen significant reductions for the operational year 1995. Chiefly responsible for this drop are modifications at the power stations which have led to a 17 percent reduction in the amount of dust emitted and a 13.4 percent fall for nitrogen oxides. In addition, the increased use of catalytic converters-as installed, for example, in the Mercedes-Benz plant in Untert&uuml;rkheim-have also helped to reduce the figures for nitrogen oxides even further.<p>The 23.5 percent reduction in sulfur dioxide emissions was achieved largely as a result of the closure of a series of coal-fired power stations at the Dasa plant in Manching, at MTU-Friedrichshafen, and in Schorch. The conversion from coal to natural gas at Manching alone has reduced sulfur dioxide emissions by 23 tonnes a year.</table><p><br><table><tr><td><td><td align=middle colspan=3 valign=bottom><b>Solvents</b><td><td align=middle colspan=3 valign=bottom><b>Dust</b><tr><td valign=bottom><font size=-1>Quantities in tonnes</font><td><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1993</b><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1994</b><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1995</b><td><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1993</b><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1994</b><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1995</b><tr><td align=right width=100 valign=top><td><tr><td colspan=9><hr><tr><tr><td align=right><B>AEG</B><td><td align=right>72<td align=right>63<td align=right>127<td><td align=right>63<td align=right>2<td align=right>3<tr><td align=right><B>DASA</B><td><td align=right>133<td align=right>133<td align=right>126<td><td align=right>19<td align=right>11<td align=right>9<tr><td align=right><B>MBAG</B><td><td align=right>4570<td align=right>3650<td align=right>4123<td><td align=right>240<td align=right>234<td align=right>193<tr><td align=right><B>DB Group</B><td><td align=right>4775<td align=right>3846<td align=right>4376<td><td align=right>322<td align=right>247<td align=right>205<tr><td colspan=9><hr></table><p><br><table><tr><td><td><td align=middle colspan=3 valign=bottom><b>Sulfur dioxides</b><td><td align=middle colspan=3 valign=bottom><b>Nitrogen oxides</b><tr><td valign=bottom><font size=-1>Quantities in tonnes</font><td><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1993</b><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1994</b><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1995</b><td><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1993</b><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1994</b><td align=right width=60 valign=bottom><b>1995</b><tr><td align=right width=100 valign=top><td><tr><td colspan=9><hr><tr><tr><td align=right><B>AEG</B><td><td align=right>540<td align=right>11<td align=right>21<td><td align=right>88<td align=right>48<td align=right>200<tr><td align=right><B>DASA</B><td><td align=right>123<td align=right>60<td align=right>15<td><td align=right>411<td align=right>410<td align=right>223<tr><td align=right><B>MBAG</B><td><td align=right>86<td align=right>48<td align=right>55<td><td align=right>599<td align=right>568<td align=right>466<tr><td align=right><B>DB Group</B><td><td align=right>749<td align=right>119<td align=right>91<td><td align=right>1098<td align=right>1026<td align=right>889<tr><td colspan=9><hr></table><IMG WIDTH=592 HEIGHT=16 SRC="../../lines/db_592.gif"><P><TABLE><TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=550><H5><A HREF="emiss_g.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Deutsch</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../index_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Home</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../envir_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Environment</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../ub96_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Environmental Report '96</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../daten_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Facts &amp; Figures</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../daten_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Next</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../search/search_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Search</I>&nbsp;]</A><A HREF="../../mail/mail_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Dialog</I>&nbsp;]</A>   <A HREF="../../help/help_e.htm">[&nbsp;<I>Help</I>&nbsp;]</A></H5></TABLE><ADDRESS>&copy; Daimler-Benz, last update: 08/06/1996</ADDRESS><P></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
